skeletonlisp.LExp
Class LError

java.lang.Object
  skeletonlisp.LExp.LExp

          skeletonlisp.LExp.LError

public class LError
extends LValue

LError contains the data-structural representation of SkeletonLisp's error expressions. However, only the interpreter really uses error expressions.
